    "intro": "Interpretation asks what the text means — moving from observation (what does it say?) to discerning the author's intent in his original context. The movements below trace the psalm's argument from its initial invocation through the vine allegory to the Messianic petition. Where the Hebrew changes the shade of an English word, a brief note follows the interpretation as supplement.",
